<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="exhausted-adj">exhausted <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ɪɡ'zɔːstɪd/    美 /ɪɡ'zɔːstɪd/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-worn-out">1.★ <strong>精疲力竭的 (worn out)；耗尽的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>an exhausted coal mine 
枯竭的煤矿</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>We were all rather exhausted when we got to the top of the mountain. 
我们到达山顶时都相当疲倦了。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>After his journey from abroad, Richard Jones returned home, <strong><em>_</em></strong> (exhaust).  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. exhausted  </p></div>